display_long_description:
Step into a VR world where fitness is gamified. Taebo Reboot brings Billy Blanks back as your coach and mentor, guiding you through over 100 challenges across the five Elemental Books; Earth, Water, Fire, Air, and Emptiness. Every strike, dodge, and block builds Precision, Agility, and Power, transforming your body and sharpening your focus with every session.

This is fitness reimagined as a game. Level up your stats, earn new belts, and unlock achievements as you progress from white to black belt. Whether you’re chasing a challenge or building consistency, Taebo Reboot makes every workout immersive, cinematic, and fun.

Train your whole body in 140+ VR workouts that mix cardio, boxing, and rhythm mechanics. Conquer the Elemental Campaign, hone your skills in Practice Mode, or go freestyle in Free Training.

With Billy’s voice motivating you and cinematic environments bringing every movement to life, you’re not just exercising, you’re evolving.

Game harder. Train smarter. Become the hero of your own story.
